{"title_page": "List of forts in India", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis is a partial '''list of [[forts in India]]'''.\n{{Expand list|date=August 2008}}\n\n== Andhra Pradesh ==\n\n=== Coastal Region ===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* [[Bellamkonda Fort]] - Guntur district\n* [[Bobbili Fort]] \u2013 Vizianagaram district\n* [[Durgam Fort]] \u2013 Prakasam district (Kanigiri)\n* [[Gajanan Fort]] \u2013 Visakhapatnam district\n* [[Gonthina Fort]] \u2013 Visakhapatnam district\n* [[Kondapalli Fort]] \u2013 Krishna district\n* [[Kondaveedu Fort]] \u2013 Guntur district\n* [[Machilipatnam Fort]] (16th century Dutch Fort)<ref>{{Citation|last=Tandavakrishna Tungala|title=Bandar Kota ( Machilipatnam Fort built by the Dutch, the French and the British )|date=2017-03-24|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iCQXXICC04w|accessdate=2017-11-21}}</ref> \u2013 Krishna district\n* [[Parth Fort]]\n* [[Udayagiri Fort]]saad - Nellore district\n* [[Venkatigiri Fort]] - Nellore district\n* [[Vizianagaram Fort]] \u2013 Vizianagaram district\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== Rayalseema Region ===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* [[Adoni Fort]] \u2013 Kurnool district\n* [[Chandragiri Fort, Andhra Pradesh|Chandragiri Fort]] \u2013 Tirupati\n* [[Chennampalli Fort]] \u2013 Kurnool district\n* [[Devaraya Fort]] \u2013 Vijayanagaram district\n* [[Gandikota Fort]] \u2013 Kadapa district\n* [[Gooty Fort]] \u2013 Anantapur district\n* [[Gurramkonda Fort]] \u2013 Chittoor district\n* [[Konda Reddy Fort]] \u2013 Kurnool district\n* [[Siddavatam Fort]] \u2013 Kadapa district\n{{div col end}}\n\n== Arunachal Pradesh ==\n* [[Ita Fort]], Itanagar\n* [[Bhismak Nagar Fort]]\n\n== Assam ==\n* [[Garchuk Lachit Garh]]\n* [[Garh Doul]]\n* [[Kareng Ghar]]\n* [[Matiabag Palace]]\n* [[Talattal Ghar]]\n\n== Bihar ==\n* [[Buxar Fort]]\n* [[Darbhanga Fort]]\n* [[Jagdishpur Fort]]\n* [[Jalalgarh Fort]]\n* [[Munger Fort]]\n* [[Rohtasgarh Fort]]\n* [[Shergarh Fort]]\n\n== Chandigarh ==\n* [[Burail For