e=\"row\"| US [[Rolling Stone Top 100|''Rolling Stone'' Top 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/charts/songs/2020-02-13/|title=Top 100 Songs|website=[[Rolling Stone]]|accessdate=February 19, 2020}}</ref>\n| 46\n|}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|type=single|award=Gold|relyear=2020|certyear=2020|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=April 13, 2020|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" |{{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| February 4, 2020\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[RCA Records|RCA]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"pitchfork\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| March 16, 2020\n| [[Adult contemporary music#Hot adult contemporary|Hot adult contemporary radio]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases|title=Hot/Modern/AC Future Releases|website=All Access|access-date=March 16, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316164807/https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases |archivedate=March 16, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Khalid}}\n{{Disclosure}}\n\n[[Category:2020 singles]]\n[[Category:2020 songs]]\n[[Category:Khalid (singer) songs]]\n[[Category:Disclosure (band) songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Jimmy Napes]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Guy Lawrence]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2020 single by Khalid and Disclosure}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Know Your Worth\n| cover      = Khalid and Disclosure - Know Your Worth.png\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid]] and [[Disclosure (band)|Disclosure]]\n| released   = {{start date|2020|2|4}}\n| format     = {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| recorded   = 2019\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Dance music|Dance]]<!-- sourced in critical reception section -->\n| length     = {{duration|m=3|s=1}}\n| label      = [[RCA Records|RCA]]\n| writer     = {{hlist|[[Khalid (singer)|Khalid Robinson]]|[[Disclosure (band)|Guy Lawrence]]|[[Jimmy Napes|James Napier]]}}\n| producer   = [[Disclosure (band)|Disclosure]]\n| chronology    = [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid]] singles\n| prev_title    = Eleven\n| prev_year     = 2020\n| next_title    =\n| next_year     =\n| misc          = {{Extra chronology\n| artist        = [[Disclosure (band)|Disclosure]] singles\n| type          = single\n| prev_title    = Where You Come From\n| prev_year     = 2018\n| title         = Know Your Worth\n| year          = 2020\n| next_title    = Ecstasy\n| next_year     = 2020\n}}\n}}\n\"'''Know Your Worth'''\" is a song by American singer [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid]] and English electronic duo [[Disclosure (band)|Disclosure]]. It was released as a single through [[RCA Records|RCA]] on February 4, 2020.<ref name=\"pitchfork\">{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/khalid-and-disclosure-share-new-song-know-your-worth-listen/|title=Khalid and Disclosure Share New Song \"Know Your Worth\": Listen|last=Hussey|first=Allison|website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|date=February 4, 2020|accessdate=February 5, 2020}}</ref> Following the 2019 song \"[[Talk (Khalid song)|Talk]]\", the song marks the second collaboration between the singer and the duo.\n\n==Background and promotion==\nAbout the song, Khalid revealed that he feels like \"the message in this song is something that I needed to hear at the time I was writing it and I hope that it resonates with a lot of people who need to hear that kind of message\".<ref name=\"billboard\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/8550100/know-your-worth-khalid-disclosure|title=Khalid Reunites With Disclosure For Uplifting \"Know Your Worth\": Listen|last=Saponara|first=Michael|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=February 4, 2020|accessdate=February 5, 2020}}</ref> Khalid announced the song through social media on January 24, 2020. The announcement was accompanied by the cover art which depicts the upper half of his face in a turquoise blue light and a clip of the chorus of the song.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B7tmalqj70u/|title=with my fam @disclosure coming very very soon more news Monday|via=[[Instagram]]|accessdate=February 5, 2020}}</ref> The song was used by [[Levi Strauss & Co.|Levi's]] for a campaign video of XX Chino.<ref name=\"complex\">{{cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2020/02/khalid-know-your-worth|title=Khalid Shares New Disclosure-Produced Track \"Know Your Worth\"|last=Gheciu|first=Alex Nino|website=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]|date=February 4, 2020|accessdate=February 5, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Critical reception==\nAlex Nino Gheciu of ''[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]'' described the song as \"a self-empowerment jam\" which \"is a decidedly more upbeat, dancefloor-ready affair\" compared to his previous single \"Eleven\".<ref name=\"complex\"/> ''[[Stereogum]]'''s Chris DeVille thought that the track is by no means a \"\"Talk\" redux\" but \"a subtly propulsive, bass-heavy dance track\" which \"is far closer to the top of his discography than the bottom\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.stereogum.com/2072380/khalid-disclosure-know-your-worth/music/|title=Khalid & Disclosure \u2013 \"Know Your Worth\"|last=DeVille|first=Chris|website=[[Stereogum]]|date=February 4, 2020|accessdate=February 5, 2020}}</ref> Michael Saponara at ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' noted that the singer \"floats over the soft electronic production with a message for a certain lover\".<ref name=\"billboard\"/>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|31|artist=Khalid & Disclosure|song=Know Your Worth|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 15, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|69|artist=Khalid & Disclosure|song=Know Your Worth|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders Tip|6|artist=Khalid & Disclosure|song=Know Your Worth|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 14, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia Tip|3|artist=Khalid & Disclosure|song=Know Your Worth|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 14, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|48|artist=Khalid|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 19, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadachrtop40|40|artist=Khalid|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 19, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czechdigital|67|year=2020|week=07|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 18, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Estonia ([[Eesti Tipp-40]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ekspress.delfi.ee/areen/eesti-tipp-40-muusikas-ohoi-parim-uus-sooritaja-on-jaapanlane-joji?id=88955427title=Eesti Tipp-40 Muusikas: Ohoi! Parim uus sooritaja on jaapanlane Joji!|language=Estonian|last=Nestor|first=Siim|website=[[Eesti Ekspress]]|date=February 18, 2020|accessdate=April 9, 2020}}</ref>\n| 22\n|-\n{{single chart|Ireland4|25|date=20200214|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 15, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lithuania ([[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.agata.lt/lt/naujienos/savaites-klausomiausi-2020w14/|title=2020 14-os savait\u0117s klausomiausi (TOP 100)|publisher=[[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]]|language=Lithuanian|date=April 3, 2020|accessdate=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n| 28\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch40|19|year=2020|week=12|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|31|artist=Khalid & Disclosure|son