r Bendtner ist zweimal zur Stelle\"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Arturo Vidal|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/1-bundesliga/2015-16/bayern-muenchen-14/44169/spieler_arturo-vidal.html|website=kicker.de |publisher=kicker |accessdate = 21 May 2016 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 FC Bayern Munich season|2016\u201317]]||27||4||5||1||8{{efn|name=UCL|Appearances in [[UEFA Champions League]]}}||3||1||1||41||9||<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/d-supercup-fb-1/2016/1/3303617/spielbericht_borussia-dortmund-17_bayern-muenchen-14.html |title = Im zweiten Anlauf: Vidal beschert Bayern den ersten Titel |language = de |website = kicker.de |date = 14 August 2016 |access-date = 14 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/1-bundesliga/2016-17/bayern-muenchen-14/44169/spieler_arturo-vidal.html |title = Arturo Vidal |language = de |website = kicker.de |access-date = 20 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 FC Bayern Munich season|2017\u201318]]||22||6||5||0||7{{efn|name=UCL|Appearances in [[UEFA Champions League]]}}||0||1||0||35||6||<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/d-supercup-fb-1/2017/1/3813700/spielbericht_borussia-dortmund-17_bayern-muenchen-14.html |title = Bayerns erster Titel dank Flippertor und Ulreich |language = de |website = kicker.de |date = 5 August 2017 |access-date = 5 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/1-bundesliga/2017-18/bayern-muenchen-14/44169/spieler_arturo-vidal.html |title = Arturo Vidal |language = de |website = kicker.de |access-date = 3 April 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Totals!!79!!14!!16!!2!!25!!5!!3!!1!!123!!22!!\u2014\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]||[[2018\u201319 FC Barcelona season|2018\u201319]]||[[La Liga]]||33||3||8||0||11{{efn|name=UCL|Appearances in [[UEFA Champions League]]}}||0||1||0||53||3|